name: Skydive Royale
description: This Skydiving Royale game is 100% free and doesn't have any advertisements or in app purchases. This game is a tribute to a very successful flash game called "Elite Base jumping" with a new spin! Your fall speed, brake speed, and impact damage all depend on the gear you have equipped. Earn coins by winning races and catching coins on your way down. Spend your coins at the shop with over 1000 combinations of gear. Battle your way up all 5 leagues. The final league is an endless mode where you try to beat the high score!
